articleTitle: "Evermore": Taylor Swift kündigt überraschend weiteres neues Album an
articleTitleTranslated: "Evermore": Taylor Swift surprisingly announces another new album
articleContent: Taylor Swift hat für die Nacht zum Freitag überraschend ihr neuntes Studioalbum angekündigt.
articleContentTranslated: Taylor Swift has surprisingly announced their ninth studio album for Friday night.
